OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772110991
OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,FA retired criminal defence solicitor
OL,7,Fhas been jailed for 13 years after
OL,8,Fsexually assaulting clients who were
OL,9,Fmostly under arrest and in custody.
OL,11,FAlan Harris, from Plymouth, carried
OL,12,Fout the majority of his abuse against
OL,13,Fseven victims during private legal
OL,14,Fconsultations at Plymouth Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt and Charles Cross Police Station
OL,16,Fin the Devon city over a time span of
OL,17,F27 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
