OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772110991
OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,FThe 72-year-old had been convicted of
OL,7,F10 offences against the six men and
OL,8,Fone woman following a five-week trial
OL,9,Fat Winchester Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe was found guilty of five counts of
OL,12,Findecent assaults and five sexual
OL,13,Fassaults, relating to incidents
OL,14,Fbetween 1988 and 2015, in December.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
