OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772110991
OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,FSentencing him at Winchester Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Wednesday, Judge Angela
OL,8,FMorris said despite Harris' outward
OL,9,Fappearance as a "thoroughly
OL,10,Frespectable" man with high regard in
OL,11,Fthe community, "there was a darker
OL,12,Fside to your character".
OL,14,FShe said: "There is no greater fall
OL,15,Ffrom grace than this.
OL,17,F"All of them had in common they had
OL,18,Fplaced their trust in you as their
OL,19,Flawyer."
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@LO]sD@POUtD@WO]vD@KOUyD@AOU{D@
OL,26,AHO]
