CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772110991
OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,FOne, directed at Harris, described how
OL,7,Fhe was the only person who could have
OL,8,Fhelped him but "you abused your
OL,9,Fposition".
OL,11,F"You are vile," he said.
OL,13,FAnother victim described being touched
OL,14,Fby Harris without their consent and
OL,15,Fsaying "no" but he "took no notice".
OL,17,F"He touched me because he felt he had
OL,18,Fthe right and the power to do so,"
OL,19,Fthey said.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@IO]sD@AOUsD@OO]wD@HOUwD@KO]wD@
OL,26,ATOUwD@cO]yD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
