FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772110991
OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,F"I was frozen to the ground in shock
OL,7,Fand used my voice to say 'no' but he
OL,8,Ftook no notice.
OL,10,F"Whatever sentence Alan Harris
OL,11,Freceives, it will never be enough for
OL,12,Fhow he has made me feel.
OL,14,F"Whatever his sentence is, I hope it
OL,15,Fis nothing less than hell because he
OL,16,Fdeserves no more than that."
OL,18,FChristine Agnew KC, representing
OL,19,FHarris, said on Tuesday her client
OL,20,Fdoes not agree with the jury's guilty
OL,21,Fverdicts but accepts them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
