OL,3,CFormer Plymouth lawyer sentenced to 13
OL,4,Cyears for sexual offences
OL,6,F"He will find it particularly
OL,7,Fdifficult to serve a custodial
OL,8,Fsentence."
OL,10,FMs Agnew added that Harris had retired
OL,11,Ffrom practicing as a solicitor in 2016.
